Text:
Thanks chkm8te, good to add some early 70's content to my library. It was before my time but i'm glad i downloaded it. Good footage of women getting right into it, not just bad acting like is usually made in the industry these days.
The resolution is ok if you keep your window small, but terrible in full screen. Do you know what format these came out on back in the day? VHS perhaps? I downloaded this on 19th May 2012 and it was fast, i'll come back and re seed over the coming week too. Much appreciated chkm8te.
